        "contentType": "text/xml",
        "isMain": true,
        "content": "<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<assessmentItem xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1 http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"composite\" title=\"Composite Item\" adaptive=\"false\" timeDependent=\"false\">\n\n    <!-- definition for question one, a short text entry response with correct answer = \"white\" -->\n    <responseDeclaration identifier=\"Q_01\" cardinality=\"single\" baseType=\"string\"> \n        <correctResponse> \n            <value>28</value> \n               \n        </correctResponse> \n    </responseDeclaration> \n   \n   <responseDeclaration identifier=\"Q_02\" cardinality=\"single\" baseType=\"identifier\">\n        <correctResponse>\n            <value>ChoiceA</value>\n        </correctResponse>\n    </responseDeclaration>\n    <outcomeDeclaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" baseType=\"integer\">\n        <defaultValue>\n            <value>0</value>\n        </defaultValue>\n    </outcomeDeclaration>\n\n      \n\n    <!-- definition for question one, a short text entry response with correct answer = \"white\" -->\n    <responseDeclaration identifier=\"Q_03\" cardinality=\"single\" baseType=\"string\"> \n        <correctResponse> \n            <value>25</value> \n        </correctResponse> \n    </responseDeclaration> \n\n    <!-- an Extended text entry response for longer form text entry -->\n    <responseDeclaration identifier=\"Q_04\" cardinality=\"single\" baseType=\"string\"/>\n\n    <itemBody>\n\n <div class=\"imagewrapper\"><img src=\"woodchess.png\"/></div>\n <div class=\"image-copyright\">Copyright 2009 cogdog</div>\n\n<h1>Where's the Best Deal?</h1>\n    <p class=\"intro-2\">Greg wants to buy a computer chess game with a regular price of $40. A hobby shop sells the computer chess game at a discounted price of 30% off the regular price. </p>\n\n    <p class=\"prompt\">What is the discounted price, in dollars, of the computer chess game at the hobby shop?</p> \n       <p> The discounted price of the chess game is $<textEntryInteraction responseIdentifier=\"Q_01\" expectedLength=\"02\"></textEntryInteraction>.00 </p>\n       \n           <feedbackBlock\n         outcomeIdentifier=\"responses.Q_01.value\"\n         identifier=\"28\">\n              <div class=\"feedback-block-correct\">Nice work, that's correct!</div>\n    </feedbackBlock>\n \n    <feedbackBlock\n         outcomeIdentifier=\"responses.Q_01.value\"\n         incorrectResponse=\"true\">\n            <div class=\"feedback-block-incorrect\">Good try! The discounted price is $28.00.</div>\n     </feedbackBlock>\n\n    <p>A department store sells the same computer chess game at a discounted price of 20% off the regular \nprice of $40. On Saturday, the department store will take an additional 10% off the already discounted \nprice of this computer chess game.</p>\n\n        <choiceInteraction responseIdentifier=\"Q_02\" shuffle=\"false\" maxChoices=\"1\">\n            <prompt>Should greg buy the computer chess game at the hobby shop or at the department store on Saturday?</prompt>\n            <simpleChoice identifier=\"ChoiceA\">Greg should buy the game at the hobby shop.\n                <feedbackInline csFeedbackId='ChoiceA' identifier='ChoiceA' showHide='show'>Correct!</feedbackInline>\n            </simpleChoice>\n            <simpleChoice identifier=\"ChoiceB\">Greg should buy the game at the department store.\n                <feedbackInline csFeedbackId='ChoiceB' identifier='ChoiceB' showHide='show'>Your answer.</feedbackInline>\n            </simpleChoice>\n        </choiceInteraction>\n        \n        \n <div class=\"imagewrapper\"><img src=\"baseballgame.png\"/></div>\n <div class=\"image-copyright\">Copyright 2006 Rafael Amado Deras</div>\n \n <h1>What's the regular price?</h1>\n <p>Later that week Greg bought a computer baseball game at the department store. The department store sold the computer baseball game at a discounted price of 20% off the regular price. The store took an additional 10% off the already discounted price. After both discounts, Greg paid $18 for the game.</p>\n    <p class=\"prompt\">What is the regular price of the computer baseball game?</p>\n        <p>The regular price is $<textEntryInteraction responseIdentifier=\"Q_03\" expectedLength=\"02\"></textEntryInteraction>.00</p>\n        \n    <feedbackBlock\n         outcomeIdentifier=\"responses.Q_03.value\"\n         identifier=\"25\">\n              <div class=\"feedback-block-correct\">Nice work, that's correct!</div>\n    </feedbackBlock>\n   \n \n    <!-- this is for any response not defined as a correct response in responseDeclaration -->\n    <feedbackBlock\n         outcomeIdentifier=\"responses.Q_03.value\"\n         incorrectResponse=\"true\">\n            <div class=\"feedback-block-incorrect\">Good try, but the regular price is $25.00</div>\n     </feedbackBlock>\n\n        <p class=\"prompt\">How do you know? Explain.</p>\n        <extendedTextInteraction responseIdentifier=\"Q_04\" expectedLength=\"200\" expectedLines=\"5\" maxStrings=\"20\" minStrings=\"10\"></extendedTextInteraction>\n\n\n\n     \n\n        \n    </itemBody>\n</assessmentItem>\n"
